title: X-Com: UFO & TFTD Total Pack
description:
X-Com: Ufo Defense and X-Com: Terror From the Deep

UFO Defense was voted the best game of all time by IGN. I personally vote X-Com TFTD as the best game ever made. You have to get over the fact that it&#039;s really old, but it&#039;s certainly worth playing in the 21st century, too.

In my country, it&#039;s legal to download this game if you own it. Last thing I checked, you can buy it with Steam as well.

Thanks a lot to starwindz for releasing this Total Pack!
